8-13T23:53:24.000Z","msg":"走啦死黑警<br />\n<br />\n之後真係走果時塞住唔比警車走<br />\n<br />\n大惑不解"},{"pid":"e400b320fc4be6c61792ed36b8e5dd39530ee71e","tid":1468920,"uid":270824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:54:38.000Z","msg":"818前。唔。好。再。入。機。場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053369d00ccc81986de67d55ef90d296c2da6644","tid":1468920,"uid":230312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:54:41.000Z","msg":"只係暫時 當政府又當和理非冇到果陣就要靠你地la勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d47c695a639833d4498d9eac2cb3f60cff889fd","tid":1468920,"uid":230312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:54:53.000Z","msg":"btw push"},{"pid":"55dc71e77ec671f7ee4607e1ab1b3f1da0351a64","tid":1468920,"uid":160074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:55:22.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅前線們，橫眉冷對千夫指，俯首甘為孺子牛。從來只有暴政，沒有暴徒，感謝勇武前線日以繼夜以命相博 ，方令暴政黑警不致對我們任意妄為，勇武派願意為我們擋子彈，那現在勇武派將面臨巨大的輿論壓力，你們會為他們擋嗎？"},{"pid":"6411df11d0c160347ba10eee735745ee6ea97e91","tid":1468920,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:55:28.000Z","msg":"勇武唔會聽你講"}]}